 Photography is the art of capturing and processing light to create images, whether using a digital sensor or film. It's more than just technical skill; it's about storytelling, preserving moments, and communicating emotions. Photography can be used to document events, capture portraits, or explore creative visions, making it a versatile and impactful medium.</p>
